---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Privacy Policy' }];
const lastUpdated = 'January 1, 2025';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | The Volleyball Uniforms"
  description="Privacy policy for The Volleyball Uniforms. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website or request a quote."
  canonical="https://thevolleyballuniforms.com/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4"><Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} /></div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy-950 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose-custom">
        <p>The Volleyball Uniforms ("we," "us," or "our") operates thevolleyballuniforms.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or contact us for services.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when you fill out our contact or quote request forms, including your name, email address, phone number, team or organization name, and details about your uniform needs. We may also automatically collect certain technical information when you visit our website, including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referring URLs through standard web analytics tools.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to respond to your quote requests and inquiries, provide design mockups and product recommendations, process and fulfill your orders, send transactional emails related to your order, improve our website and services, and comply with applicable legal requirements. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience and analyze site traffic. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent. However, if you do not accept cookies, some portions of our website may not function properly.</p>

        <h2>Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website and conducting our business, such as email service providers and production management software. These parties are contractually required to keep your information confidential and use it only for the services they provide to us. We may also disclose your information if required by law, court order, or other governmental authority.</p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information, request restriction of processing, and object to processing. To exercise these rights, contact us at Info@thevolleyballuniforms.com.</p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not directed to children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Your continued use of our website after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br />
        The Volleyball Uniforms<br />
        245 W 29th St, New York, NY 10001<br />
        Email: Info@thevolleyballuniforms.com<br />
        Phone: +1 212-555-0198</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
